  stimulus_text = 'The author’s intent is to highlight the complex relationship between humans and their environment.  The author points to the ways that human interactions with nature can shape our understanding of the natural world.  The text suggests that humans are not separate from nature, and that our relationship with it is dynamic and constantly evolving. The author asks the reader to consider how our actions can impact the environment and how our perceptions of nature can be shaped by our experiences. What is the author''s main point in the passage?',
